            <img class="c-newstickerarticle__img lazyload" data-sizes="46px" data-srcset="https://images.tijd.be/view?iid=Elvis:1le-Lm6l4uwA9lwAer_WlP&amp;context=ONLINE&amp;ratio=4/3&amp;width=240&amp;u=1611937187000 240w, https://images.tijd.be/view?iid=Elvis:1le-Lm6l4uwA9lwAer_WlP&amp;context=ONLINE&amp;ratio=4/3&amp;width=640&amp;u=1611937187000 640w, https://images.tijd.be/view?iid=Elvis:1le-Lm6l4uwA9lwAer_WlP&amp;context=ONLINE&amp;ratio=4/3&amp;width=815&amp;u=1611937187000 815w, https://images.tijd.be/view?iid=Elvis:1le-Lm6l4uwA9lwAer_WlP&amp;context=ONLINE&amp;ratio=4/3&amp;width=1024&amp;u=1611937187000 1024w, https://images.tijd.be/view?iid=Elvis:1le-Lm6l4uwA9lwAer_WlP&amp;context=ONLINE&amp;ratio=4/3&amp;width=1280&amp;u=1611937187000 1280w"/>
        </div>
        <div class="c-newstickerarticle__content">
            
            <div class="c-newstickerarticle__title gtm-newsticker-article-title">Europees groen licht voor AstraZeneca-vaccin</div>
        </div>
    </a>
</div></div>
</div>
    
        <div class="c-newstickerlist__item"><div class="article base page basicpage">
